11
00:00:39,200 --> 00:00:41,520
One of them I could say, build the back end.

12
00:00:41,520 --> 00:00:43,759
And one of them I could say, build the tests.

13
00:00:43,759 --> 00:00:47,360
And as long as I've done a good enough job of identifying the boundaries

14
00:00:47,360 --> 00:00:52,240
and how they'll work together, they would probably just all work in parallel.

15
00:00:52,240 --> 00:00:55,439
It's a great example of the dangers of chaos

16
00:00:55,439 --> 00:00:59,279
